ground. Get to within 10-15 feet of the middle,

00:01:16.210 --> 00:01:23.110
that's good enough, I'm going to take this
off, hold the middle in my hand, grab out

00:01:23.110 --> 00:01:34.930
here, wrap it up.
We're almost done, going to take a bite of

00:01:34.930 --> 00:01:45.540
this doubled rope, pass it through, cinch
it up, pull the end through, there you go.

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:49.820
One more thing you can do with this, you're
going to stuff it in your backpack, just take

00:01:49.820 --> 00:01:55.160
